{"tid":2223173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家樂經理欺壓員工(救助)","createTime":"2020-09-29T15:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T08:14:00.000Z","uid":313620,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4e19449acea977a3e0b36ba7affe76a2893be063","tid":2223173,"uid":313620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T15:22:40.000Z","msg":"有位屋企人做大家樂好多年，工時長不得只，大家樂經理處處針對，成日叫人去洗碗，但工作崗位並不包括洗碗。曾經要求過，只做原來工作嘅單位，就被即時放假。<br />\n<br />\n近日中秋節，公司有一些給員工的過節獎勵，大家樂經理竟然刻意沒有派俾我屋企人，但給所有其他員工。<br />\n<br />\nVery sad."},{"pid":"10460c20816c878f843d275c491bbd2591c4b95e","tid":2223173,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T15:41:37.000Z","msg":"針對處處有，不如辭職吧啦，搵過份比較好，但依家咁環境因素要注意"},{"pid":"fe9ca2848902f820c451252d1dff752f44054527","tid":2223173,"uid":313620,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"10460c20816c878f843d275c491bbd2591c4b95e","tid":2223173,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T15:41:37.000Z","msg":"針對處處有，不如辭職吧啦，搵過份比較好，但依家咁環境因素要注意"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:07:53.000Z","msg":"帥兄，你的意見好無意義。"},{"pid":"f100b91eefa3df79314bef2862671199495e6095","tid":2223173,"uid":21901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:16:53.000Z","msg":"邊間大記啊"},{"pid":"22514fcec1c9da614a77e4807cc60c23d64ee450","tid":2223173,"uid":34047,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:22:19.000Z","msg":"如果係公司規矩每個員工都有<br />\n但就係唔比你屋企人<br />\n真係好有問題"},{"pid":"262ca51acf9a07776522b7eb326c75c32c08a6fb","tid":2223173,"uid":313620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f100b91eefa3df79314bef2862671199495e6095","tid":2223173,"uid":21901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:16:53.000Z","msg":"邊間大記啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:23:45.000Z","msg":"分店？"},{"pid":"706484fbf57e0bd607ede0808139488df1d51281","tid":2223173,"uid":313620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f100b91eefa3df79